scene.message:
Yukino: "Mirror Shards" can{nl}
be in treasure chests too,{nl}
you know!!

Ayase: Same as always, but{nl}
opening a treasure chest is{nl}
always a thrill, right!

Nanjo: Somehow, the sight of{nl}
rummaging through chests{nl}
isn't a becoming one for a{nl}
human.{waitkey}{clearbox}No, I'm not talking about you{nl}
in particular. It's purely a{nl}
general observation. Mm.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Hey, you, you're{nl}
always so quiet, so honestly{nl}
I thought you were a weird{waitkey}guy...{waitkey}{clearbox}But after fighting alongside{nl}
you, I get it now!! You're{nl}
amazing!!{waitkey}{clearbox}You're about the second{nl}
strongest after me, and about{nl}
the second most reliable!{waitkey}I've got new respect for you!!{nl}
Really.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: I've gained a little{nl}
new respect for you. Even in{nl}
a situation like this,{waitkey}{clearbox}without a single complaint{nl}
you hold everyone together...{nl}
To think you possessed such a{nl}
strong BraveHeart{waitkey}all along.{waitkey}{ret}
